MakeGeoURL <- function(address){
  root <- "https://geocode.maps.co/search"
  url  <- paste0(root, "?q={", address, "}")
  return(URLencode(url))
}
#fromJSON(apiResult,simplifyVector = FALSE)
Addr2latlng <- function(address) {
  url <- MakeGeoURL(address)
  apiResult <- getURL(url)
  geoStruct <- fromJSON(apiResult,simplifyVector = FALSE)
  lat <- NA
  lng <- NA
  try(lat <- as.numeric(geoStruct[[1]]$lat))
  try(lng <- as.numeric(geoStruct[[1]]$lon))
  Sys.sleep(1) #Limit our requests to one per second
  return(c(lat, lng))
}

ProcessAddrList = function(addrList){
  resultDF = data.frame(atext=character(), X=numeric(),Y=numeric(), EID=numeric())
  i = 1
  for (addr in addrList)
    {
    latlng = Addr2latlng(addr)
    resultDF = rbind(resultDF, data.frame(atext=addr, X=latlng[[2]], Y=latlng[[1]], EID=i))
    i = i+1
    
  }
  return(resultDF)
}
